This is a "plugin" for the Video Disk Recorder (VDR).

Written by:                  Werner Sigrist <sigvdr@online.de>

Project's homepage:          http://www.cl-si.de

Latest version available at: http://www.cl-si.de/vdrinfo

See the file COPYING for license information.



Description:
##########################################################
This plugin shows infos from VDR over SVDRP.
Mainly used for EasyStream a VDR Streaming-Client. 

DEVICES:    		return the number of devices found by VDR

RECSTATUS:  		return the status of recordings
        		0 -> no recodring
			1 -> recording
			2 -> recording on all devices  
	    
DEVSTATUS <device>:	return the current recordings and the current channel 
			of a selected device. For example:
			"202 Device 0: Rec=2 Used=7"
			On device 0 are current 2 recordings and the device 
			is switched to channel 7. 